sequenceDiagram
    participant PO as Product Owner
    participant Archive as Archive System
    participant HUPlan as hu-work-planner
    participant Gimena as gimena-scheduler
    participant Teams as Development Teams

    Note over PO,Teams: PLANNING PHASE - WORK SCHEDULER SYSTEM
    
    PO->>Archive: Submit planning inputs (single request)
    Note right of Archive: Inputs Archived:<br/>- Conversation .txt<br/>- Database design.sql<br/>- Architecture docs<br/>- Technical notes
    
    Archive->>HUPlan: Forward all planning inputs
    
    activate HUPlan
    Note right of HUPlan: HU Generation Process
    
    HUPlan->>HUPlan: 1. Analyze all inputs
    HUPlan->>HUPlan: 2. Extract requirements
    HUPlan->>HUPlan: 3. Generate HUs for ALL modules
    HUPlan->>HUPlan: 4. Create HU files structure
    
    HUPlan->>Gimena: Submit consolidated HUs (all modules)
    deactivate HUPlan
    
    activate Gimena
    Note right of Gimena: Schedule Validation & Creation
    
    Gimena->>Gimena: 1. Validate consolidated HUs
    Gimena->>Gimena: 2. Organize by modules
    Gimena->>Gimena: 3. Analyze task dependencies
    Gimena->>Gimena: 4. Allocate resources (Backend/Frontend)
    Gimena->>Gimena: 5. Set time projections per module:
    Note right of Gimena: Time Allocation Example:<br/>Module A:<br/>- Backend: 6h<br/>- Frontend: 6h<br/>- Planning: 1.5h<br/>- Integration: 2.5h<br/>- Deployment: 1.5h<br/><br/>Module B:<br/>- Backend: 8h<br/>- Frontend: 8h<br/>- Planning: 2h<br/>- Integration: 3h<br/>- Deployment: 2h
    
    Gimena->>Gimena: 6. Create milestone timeline:
    Note right of Gimena: Project Milestones:<br/>Phase 1: Planning + Module A Backend start<br/>Phase 2: Module A complete + Module B start<br/>Phase 3: Module B complete + Integration<br/>Phase 4: Testing + Deployment
    
    Gimena->>Gimena: 7. Generate complete schedule document:
    Note right of Gimena: Schedule Includes:<br/>- Modules breakdown<br/>- HUs per module<br/>- Timing & hour estimates<br/>- Project phases/milestones<br/>- Resource allocation
    
    Gimena-->>PO: Complete Schedule Document
    deactivate Gimena
    
    PO->>Teams: Distribute schedule to development teams
